effect_freeze
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
effect_freeze

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
effect_freeze -  This method freezes all the current effects so that they do not continue to be processed.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void effect_freeze()
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/effects.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method freezes all the current effects so that they do
not continue to be processed.  Basicly it removes the call_out
for the effect_timer().  It also ensures the intrval for the
immediately pending effect
is correct.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
effect_timer(), add_effect()

.EP

